      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BONA KHAN (4) is in terrific form having landed a winning a hat trick by coming form wider and digging deep to get home by a head here last week. Should enjoy a nice run from a more favourable starting position so could extend the winning streak. BREATHE EASY (3) is back from an eight-week let up but was racing consistently prior, placing in five of his last six outings. Came from this barrier to be beaten only 1.6m at this circuit and distance when last seen. Big chance. BETTORSWEETVICTORY (2) was a Bendigo winner last month and looks close to another success after placing in his last three outings, beaten 3.8m into second after racing parked here last time. Should get every chance from the ace draw. ALL THINGS SPICY (9) will be fitter for two outings off a spell, coming from this row to go under by 4.5m at this circuit and distance last time. Won the only other time he attempted this trip. Could peak. Tricky draw for BAYSTYLE (10) but his best form measures right up.",
